INSERT INTO `oc_categories` VALUES(6, 1, '1', '1', 0, 'Childcare courses', '', 'childcare-courses', 6, '<div align="justify"><table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"><tbody><tr><td width="50%"><h3><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</span></span></h3></td><td><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</span></span></td><td width="50%"><h3><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</span></span></h3></td></tr><tr><td><div align="justify"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="line-height: 115%;"><font size="2" face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" color="#666666">We are really proud of the wide selection of childcare courses that are available for students wishing to learn from home. Whether you are a complete beginner or wanting increase and improve on knowledge already gained, we have a childcare course which will be appropriate to your requirements. By studying from home the work will be able to be fitted around family or other commitments. Another great advantage is that whichever course is chosen can be started during any month in the year, rather than the usual start in September if the course is being taken at college.</font></span></span></span></div></td><td><p align="justify"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font size="2" face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" color="#666666">&nbsp;</font></span></span></p></td><td><div align="justify"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font size="2" face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" color="#666666">There isn’t the need to attend lecturers or tutorials and the student can work at their own speed, knowing that there is full support available from the advisors at UK Open College. Full course material is provided for every childcare course and there is no requirement to have any knowledge before commencing the work. Once the decision has been made to start a childcare course the first thing is to enrol and pay the course fee. All coursework will then be delivered within seven days. There is also a seven day money back guarantee available for every new student.</font></span></span></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p align="justify"><font size="2" face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" color="#666666">The many benefits available from taking a childcare course from UK Open College really do mean that the course revolves around the timetable of the student rather than the reverse, which is the usual situation. If, for any reason, it isn’t possible to study when planned, for instance, if a family member is ill or an unexpected emergency crops up, then that work is able to be rescheduled for another day later in the week, or even next week, if necessary. Obviously, once the decision has been taken to start the course it is recommended that the study is regularly undertaken – however, if essential, plans can be changed.</font></p>', '', 0, 'ID-10093867.jpg', '', '', '', '2013-06-26 23:11:45', '0');
INSERT INTO `oc_categories` VALUES(8, 14, '1', '1', 0, 'GCSE / IGCSE Courses', '', 'gcse-igcse-courses', 29, '<font size="2" face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" color="#666666"><br />New to the UK Open College are a range of IGCSE courses to be studied via distance learning. Seen as an ideal follow up to students wishing to progress onto A Level studies and then university IGCSE courses are an invaluable qualification to hold. Provided in paper format, provided in sturdy, quality ring binders and delivered direct to your door within 7 days of enrolment. <strong>Studying for your IGCSE certification could not be simpler!<br /><br /></strong>A full range of courses are now on offer covering a variety of subjects to suit all requirements. IGCSE Maths and <a href="http://www.ukopencollege.co.uk/igcse-first-language-english-course-p-1767.html" title="GCSE English">IGCSE English</a> will always prove to be important qualifications to hold and the majority of employers will look for competency in both of these areas as standard. For all those budding entrepeneurs we offer an IGCSE in Business Studies covering a whole range of business related subjects to help prepare you for further study or any business venture you may be considering.<br /><br />We offer one or two other fascinating subjects such as IGCSE Travel &amp; Tourism, <a href="http://www.ukopencollege.co.uk/igse-history-course-p-1769.html" title="GCSE History">IGCSE History</a> and <a href="http://www.ukopencollege.co.uk/igcse-geography-course-p-1768.html" title="GCSE Geograpy">IGCSE Geography</a>. You may want to consider combining one or two of these subjects as they compliment each other quite nicely. For those of you looking form something a little different take a look at our IGCSE Sociology or even our <a href="http://www.ukopencollege.co.uk/igcse-chemistry-course-p-1766.html" title="GCSE Chemistry">IGCSE Chemistry</a> and <a href="http://www.ukopencollege.co.uk/igcse-biology-course-p-1765.html" title="GCSE Biology">IGSCE Biology courses</a>. All of these courses are extremely interesting and students could find these a huge help in progressing into higher education in the future.<br /><br />Whatever you decide or if you need help or advice in selecting the right course please feel free to contact our friendly team on 0800 0131030.<br /><br /></font>', '', 0, NULL, '', '', '', '2013-06-26 23:11:47', '0');
